{"tid":2034401,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"「召喚科大人旁聽」聽日兩點半校長論壇衝突案再次提堂","createTime":"2020-05-25T08:18:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T08:41:10.000Z","uid":173531,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"08fc6b8c77a1e25df9d9912246e58d23a47135c4","tid":2034401,"uid":173531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T08:18:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CAaQ1iPhpac/?igshid=hx00keaab9ai\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCAaQ1iPhpac%2F%3Figshid%3Dhx00keaab9ai&d=g30fgRh1OaLpBbOto8aU3kwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=68d76ea9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCAaQ1iPhpac%2F%3Figshid%3Dhx00keaab9ai&h=b37d11f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CAaQ1iPhpac/?igshid=hx00keaab9ai</a><br />\n【校長論壇衝突案被捕科大生下週二再次提堂】<br />\n一名科大同學涉嫌於校長論壇與他人發生碰撞被警方登門拘捕。同學被控「傷人或對他人身體加以嚴重傷害」，將於五月二十六日（下週二）下午兩時半在東區裁判法院一號庭再次提堂，本會呼籲科大人到場旁聽支持。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日記得去支持俾屎維搞9嘅手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"1e64394ecbc68731f709c96b1c0ab0ae2b180d9a","tid":2034401,"uid":173531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T08:23:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">兩點半東區法院一號庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"2b443b12ab5857006db3f44f327358ee85d7d405","tid":2034401,"uid":173531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T08:41:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">兩點半東區法院一號庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"}]}